startGameIncome().details: Function that starts the game, income will begin to be calculated and received (this happens by chaning the 'gameStart' value to current block.timestamp and setting at 'lastPay' for all cities)

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

upgradeBuilding(uint256,uint256,uint256).details: Function upgrading a building at the index in the list

params.buildingIndex: the index of the building in the list
params.price: the price of upgrading the building
